Slide 2: Executive Summary

Objective: Comparative review of market-leading ASV solutions for banking-grade fraud detection.
+4

Key Themes:

Transition from rule-based to AI-driven models.
+1

Hybrid architectures: Combining geometric, neural, and document forensics.
+4

Consortium intelligence as a "shared immune system".
